hopobject.body: I work with computers gear199.com reviews Vonn blew out her right knee Feb. 5 in the super-G at the world championships in Schladming, Austria. She previously targeted World Cup downhill, super-G and giant slalom races at Beaver Creek, Nov. 29-Dec. 1 for her return to competition, but she's heading to Europe in a couple of weeks and may race the season-opening World Cup GS race, Oct. 26 in Soelden, Austria.
